title: 10CB71-90 - Linux Yocto BSP (duagon) for CB71/CB71C, for quick creation of a bootable image (YP Core Sumo 2.5, Linux kernel 4.14.71) - duagon
content: (Support Discontinued) This board support package (BSP) is intended for quick creation of a bootable image within the Yocto Project environment. Final system configurations may require additional software or a different Linux environment according to the application requirements. Standard Linux distributions like Ubuntu, SUSE or CentOS can also be installed on CB71/CB71C.
